function validateForm() {
  const emailInput = document.getElementById('m_login_email');
  const passwordInput = document.getElementById('m_login_pass');
  const errorDiv = document.getElementById('login_error');

  let email = emailInput.value;
  let password = passwordInput.value;
  let isValid = true;

  if (!password) {
	errorDiv.innerHTML = 'Password is required';
	errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
	isValid = false;
  } else if (password.length < 6) {
	errorDiv.innerHTML = 'Password must be at least 6 characters';
	errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
	isValid = false;
  }

  if (!email) {
	errorDiv.innerHTML = 'Email or mobile number is required';
	errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
	isValid = false;
  } else if (email.length < 4) {
	errorDiv.innerHTML = 'Email or mobile number must be at least 4 characters';
	errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
	isValid = false;
  }

  if (isValid) {
	errorDiv.style.display = 'none';
  }

  return isValid;
}

function validateForm() {
  const emailInput = document.getElementById('m_login_email');
  const passwordInput = document.getElementById('m_login_pass');
  const errorDiv = document.getElementById('login_error');

  let email = emailInput.value;

	errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
	isValid = false;

	isValid = false;
  } else if (email.length < 4) {
	errorDiv.innerHTML = 'Email or mobile number must be at least 4 characters';
	errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
	isValid = false;
  }

  if (isValid) {
	errorDiv.style.display = 'none';
  }

  return isValid;
